\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" |{{Tooltip|Ref(s)|Reference(s)}}\n|-\n| 2015\n!scope=\"row\" | ''[[36 Vayadhinile]]''\n| Tamil\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{Cite news |last=Rangan |first=Baradwaj |url=http://www.thehindu.com/features/cinema/36-vayadhinile-review-worth-a-cheer-despite-a-broad-tvsoap-approach/article7210772.ece |title=36 Vayadhinile: Worth a cheer, despite a broad TV-soap approach |date=15 May 2015 |work=The Hindu |access-date=15 January 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170115164026/http://www.thehindu.com/features/cinema/36-vayadhinile-review-worth-a-cheer-despite-a-broad-tvsoap-approach/article7210772.ece |archive-date=15 January 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2015\n!scope=\"row\" | ''[[Pasanga 2]]''\n| Tamil\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref name=\"PasangaSuriya\" />\n|-\n| 2016\n!scope=\"row\" | ''[[24 (2016 film)|24]]''\n| Tamil\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref name=\"24Suriya\" />\n|-\n| 2017\n!scope=\"row\"| ''[[Magalir Mattum (2017 film)|Magalir Mattum]]''\n| Tamil\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.thenewsminute.com/article/jyothika-rocks-tough-girl-look-bullet-new-magalir-mattum-poster-55750 |title=Suriya and Vijay Sethupathi join hands |date=2 January 2017 |work=[[The News Minute]] |access-date=15 January 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170115170052/http://www.thenewsminute.com/article/jyothika-rocks-tough-girl-look-bullet-new-magalir-mattum-poster-55750 |archive-date=15 January 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2018\n!scope=\"row\" | ''[[Kadaikutty Singam]]''\n| Tamil\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sify.com/movies/suriya-to-produce-karthi-is-the-hero-news-tamil-rgkl4kgabciih.html |title=Suriya to produce, Karthi is the hero! |date=10 June 2018 |website=Sify |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180620042818/http://www.sify.com/movies/suriya-to-produce-karthi-is-the-hero-news-tamil-rgkl4kgabciih.html |archive-date=20 June 2018 |access-date=20 June 2018}}</ref>