usamy\n|{{sort|Anand|[[K. V. Anand]]}}\n| Tamil\n| Nominated\u2014Filmfare Award for Best Actor&nbsp;\u2013 Tamil\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rediff.com/movies/2009/apr/03review-ayan.htm |title=Ayan is a must-watch |last=Srinivasan |first=Pavithra |date=3 April 2009 |website=Rediff.com |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170115134254/http://www.rediff.com/movies/2009/apr/03review-ayan.htm |archive-date=15 January 2017 |access-date=15 January 2017}}</ref><br /><ref>{{Cite episode |title=57th Filmfare Awards South |series=Filmfare Awards South |network=[[The Times Group]] |date=7 August 2010}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2009\n!scope=\"row\" | ''[[Aadhavan]]''\n| Madhavan Subramaniam (Aadhavan, Murugan){{efn|name=character}}\n|{{sort|Ravikumar|[[K. S. Ravikumar]]}}\n| Tamil\n|\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sify.com/movies/aadhavan-review-tamil-pclxskdcdgdgd.html |title=Aadhavan |date=17 October 2009 |website=Sify |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170115133041/http://www.sify.com/movies/aadhavan-review-tamil-pclxskdcdgdgd.html |archive-date=15 January 2017 |access-date=15 January 2017}}</ref><br /><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://upperstall.com/film/aadhavan/ |title=Aadhavan |last=Kingston |first=Daya |year=2009 |website=Upperstall.com |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171202144833/http://upperstall.com/film/aadhavan/ |archive-date=2 December 2017 |access-date=2 December 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2010\n!scope=\"row\" | ''[[Singam]]''\n| Duraisingam\n|[[Hari (director)|Hari]]\n| Tamil\n| Nominated\u2014Filmfare Award for Best Actor&nbsp;\u2013 Tamil\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{Cite news |last=Ravi |first=Bhama Devi |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/tamil/movie-reviews/Singam/movie-review/5987899.cms |title=Singam Movie Review |date=29 May 2010 |work=The Times of India |access-date=15 January 2017 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://archive.is/20170115163419/http://timesofi