eb.archive.org/web/20170329104449/http://www.sify.com/movies/kadugu-to-release-on-march-24-imagegallery-kollywood-rdwq0Sdjhfieb.html |archive-date=29 March 2017 |access-date=29 March 2017}}</ref><br /><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/tamil/music/vijay-miltons-kadugu-has-a-unique-audio-launch/articleshow/57646459.cms |title=Vijay Milton's Kadugu has a unique audio launch |date=15 March 2017 |work=The Times of India |access-date=29 March 2017 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20170329104505/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/tamil/music/vijay-miltons-kadugu-has-a-unique-audio-launch/articleshow/57646459.cms |archive-date=29 March 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2019\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Sillu Karupatti]]''\n| Distributor\n| Tamil\n|\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/regional-movies/suriya-jyothika-throw-a-party-to-celebrate-50-day-run-of-sillu-karuppatti-see-pics/story-d0Eo44lZhLvKPdZZ4jX5SL.html |title=Suriya, Jyothika throw a party to celebrate 50-day run of Sillu Karuppatti, see pics |date=2020-02-24 |work=Hindustan Times |access-date=2020-03-26}}</ref>\n|}\n\n== Discography ==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\" style=\"margin-right: 0;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" |Year\n! scope=\"col\"|Film\n! scope=\"col\"|Song\n! scope=\"col\"|Language(s)\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\"|Notes\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\"|{{Tooltip|Ref(s)|Reference(s)}}\n|-\n| 2014\n!scope=\"row\" | ''[[Anjaan (2014 film)|Anjaan]]''\n| \"[[Anjaan (soundtrack)|Ek Do Theen Char]]\"\n| Tamil\n| Co-sang with [[Andrea Jeremiah]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref name=\"Anjaan\" />\n|-\n| 2019\n!scope=\"row\" | ''[[Party (upcoming film)|Party]]''\n| \"Cha Cha Charey\"\n| Tamil\n| Co-sang with [[Karthi]], [[Kharesma Ravichandran]], [[Venkat Prabhu]] and [[Premgi Amaren]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{Cite web |url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/cha-cha-charey-from-party-sing